description:
The story of Jacob, his multiple wives and sons has many lessons for us today. However, the story of his favourite son, Joseph, certainly stands out the most. From Joseph's favoured position in his father's home, to being sold as a slave, from Potiphar's house to the prison, and then to Pharaoh's palace. His life saw a huge change in fortune, yet his honour, virtue and dignity remained steadfast throughout.
